com.crawljax.oraclecomparator

Class AbstractComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.crawljax.oraclecomparator.AbstractComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributeComparator, EditDistanceComparator, PlainStructureComparator, RegexComparator, ScriptComparator, SimpleComparator, StyleComparator, XPathExpressionComparator

    @NotThreadSafe
public abstract class AbstractComparator
extends Object
implements Comparator
    The Abstract base class of all the Comparators. All comparators are not Thread safe as comparators are shared between Threads and the origionalDom and newDom can not be final.
